00:14:22.260 --> 00:14:25.609
to share and combine their talents and passions."
去分享并融合他们的才能和激情。“

278
00:14:25.609 --> 00:14:28.739
If some of you are worrying now that you don't work at a Pixar,
如果你们其中的一些人 在担心你们没有在Pixar上班，

