00:14:28.739 --> 00:14:30.379
or you don't work at a Google,
或者不在Google工作，

280
00:14:30.379 --> 00:14:32.820
I want to tell you there's still hope.
我想告诉你们，仍然有改进的空间。

281
00:14:32.820 --> 00:14:34.820
We've studied many organizations
我们也研究了很多并不是

