取而代之的是，他们开始发现

306
00:15:51.499 --> 00:15:55.376
the people at the bottom of the pyramid, the young sparks,
在金字塔底层的，年轻的，

307
00:15:55.376 --> 00:15:57.850
the people who were closest to the customers,
与客户最亲近的人，

